Absolutely counting down the days that I’m back on that magical island!! Words and pictures don’t do it justice. It has to be seen and taken in to fully understand  the beauty. I truly wish everyone got to experience the amazing places our planet has to offer. Traveling and immersing yourself into different cultures is such a humbling and growing experience. I think about Oahu almost daily. #earth #travel #live #wish #hawaii #oahu #northshore
